{"word":"G1956 - ἐπιλύω - epilýō - ep-ee-loo'-o - Determine","slug":"G1956","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπιλύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>epilýō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ep-ee-loo'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Determine"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"- Original: <b><el>ἐπιλύω</el></b> <p />- Transliteration: <b>Epiluo</b> <p />- Phonetic: <b>ep-ee-loo'-o</b> <p class=\"def\">- Definition: </p> <p class='li260'><b>1.</b> to unloose, untie </p> <p class='li260'><b>2.</b> to clear (a controversy), decide, settle </p> <p class='li260'><b>3.</b> to explain (what is obscure and hard to understand) </p> <p class=\"origin\"/>- Origin: from <a href=\"#/G1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G3089\">G3089</a> <p />- TDNT entry: 09:37,5 <p />- Part(s) of speech: Verb <p />- Strong's: From <a href=\"#/G1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G3089\">G3089</a>; to <i>solve further</i> that is (figuratively) to <i>explain</i> <b><i>decide</i></b>: - determine expound. "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G179\">G179</a>, <a href=\"#/G1955\">G1955</a>, <a href=\"#/G2646\">G2646</a>, <a href=\"#/G2647\">G2647</a>, <a href=\"#/G3083\">G3083</a>, <a href=\"#/G3084\">G3084</a>, <a href=\"#/G3085\">G3085</a>, <a href=\"#/G3086\">G3086</a>, <a href=\"#/G3089\">G3089</a>, <a href=\"#/G359\">G359</a>, <a href=\"#/G360\">G360</a>, <a href=\"#/G487\">G487</a>, <a href=\"#/G629\">G629</a>, <a href=\"#/G630\">G630</a>"}]}